tps://www.isitwp.com/?p=227004\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:619:\"<p>Want to create a content upgrade for your WordPress website? That&#8217;s a fantastic idea! Content upgrades are the perfect way to transform a regular post or page into a powerful lead magnet. Gain more subscribers, increase your downloads, or even turn readers into customers! In this post, we&#8217;ll show you how to create a content [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-content-upgrade/\">How to Create a High-Conversion Content Upgrade (Easy Way)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10931:\"<p>Want to create a content upgrade for your WordPress website? That&#8217;s a fantastic idea! Content upgrades are the perfect way to transform a regular post or page into a powerful lead magnet. Gain more subscribers, increase your downloads, or even turn readers into customers!</p>\n<p>In this post, we&#8217;ll show you how to create a content upgrade, step-by-step, with pictures.</p>\n<h3>What&#8217;s a Content Upgrade?</h3>\n<p>A content upgrade is a lead magnet, also known as optin bribe, you offer within your article to encourage your visitors to subscribe to your list. The content upgrade offer is usually highlighted text inside the content area of your blog. </p>\n<p>Here&#8217;s how a content upgrade looks like&#8230; See the screenshot. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/content-upgrade.png\" alt=\"content upgrade\" width=\"615\" height=\"334\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-228070\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/content-upgrade.png 615w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/content-upgrade-300x163.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 615px) 100vw, 615px\" /></p>\n<p>When a user clicks on the link, a popup will be triggered, asking the user to subscribe to the email list.</p>\n<p>Did you know that compared to a typical lead generation campaign, content upgrade can <a href=\"https://syedbalkhi.com/how-i-increased-conversions-by-845-with-a-simple-psychology-trick/\" target=\"_blank\">grow your conversions by 865%</a>?  </p>\n<p>There are 3 reasons why a content upgrade outperforms other lead generation forms.</p>\n<p><strong>Reason #1: Targeted Resource</strong></p>\n<p>Unlike typical lead magnet you promote on blog sidebar, a content upgrade offer is catered especially for the readers of that particular post or page. Since it offers a targeted resource, users are more likely to subscribe to that offer. </p>\n<p>For example, if you run a blog about dogs, your &#8220;generic&#8221; freebie you offer on sidebar, might be an eBook on the <em>10 Best Dog Foods for Any Breed</em>. However, if you write a post specifically about potty training a puppy, you could include a content upgrade freebie / optin for a checklist of the <em>5 Steps to Tame the Tinkle</em>. Make sense? Not every reader is going to be interested in potty training a puppy; however, the people who are reading that particular blog post are absolutely going to want that specifically-catered content upgrade.</p>\n<p><strong>Reason #2: Grabs Attention Easily</strong></p>\n<p>Visitors tend to ignore opt-ins displayed on your blog posts due to banner blindness. Since content upgrade offers are usually placed within an article, they&#8217;re more likely to grab attention of your visitors. </p>\n<p><strong>Reason #3: Zeigarnik Effect </strong></p>\n<p>According to a psychological principle, Zeigarnik effect, people who initiate a process are more likely to finish it. </p>\n<p>In this case, your content upgrade comes in the form of a link. Once your reader clicks that link, an optin popup for your newsletter / free eBook / other offer comes up. Since the reader has already initiated the process by clicking the link, they&#8217;re more likely to obey your call-to-action and do whatever the optin popup tells them to.</p>\n<p>The good news is, it&#8217;s really easy to create a content upgrade for your WordPress website! Let&#8217;s jump in.</p>\n<h3>Step 1: Create a Popup Campaign</h3>\n<p>Since content upgrades are all about amazing popups, you&#8217;ll need the right tool to get started. We highly recommend signing up for <a href=\"https://optinmonster.com\" target=\"_blank\">OptinMonster</a>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/optinmonster.jpg\" alt=\"OptinMonster\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-224558\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/optinmonster.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/optinmonster-300x135.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/optinmonster-768x347.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>OptinMonster is the world&#8217;s best lead generation tool for WordPress websites. You&#8217;ll be able to create beautiful, eye-catching popup campaigns with irresistible call-to-action messages. Your subscriber list is sure to skyrocket!</p>\n<p>Better still, IsItWP readers get 10% off when they use the coupon code <strong>SAVE10</strong> when checking out.</p>\n<p>Once you have OptinMonster, follow our easy step-by-step tutorial on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-popup-form/\" title=\"How to Create a Popup Form\">how to create a popup form</a>. </p>\n<p>Now it&#8217;s time to turn that campaign into a content upgrade. Let&#8217;s move onto step 2 to learn exactly how to do that.</p>\n<h3>Step 2: Get a MonsterLink</h3>\n<p>Start by clicking the <strong>Display Rules</strong> tab at the top of your screen.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Display-Rules-1.png\" alt=\"Display Rules\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-227032\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Display-Rules-1.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Display-Rules-1-300x132.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Display-Rules-1-768x337.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>From there, click on the dropdown menu and select <strong>Visitor Clicked MonsterLink</strong>.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Clicked-MonsterLink.png\" alt=\"Clicked MonsterLink\" width=\"775\" height=\"203\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-227040\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Clicked-MonsterLink.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Clicked-MonsterLink-300x79.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Clicked-MonsterLink-768x201.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Save your campaign by clicking the green <strong>Save</strong> button in the top right-hand corner.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Save-Campaign-1.png\" alt=\"Save Campaign\" width=\"775\" height=\"72\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-227042\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Save-Campaign-1.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Save-Campaign-1-300x28.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Save-Campaign-1-768x71.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Now, go to the <strong>Publish</strong> tab. Once there, toggle your campaign to the <strong>Live</strong> position.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Publish-1.png\" alt=\"Publish\" width=\"775\" height=\"361\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-227083\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Publish-1.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Publish-1-300x140.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Publish-1-768x358.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Click <strong>Save</strong>. Keep this page open in your browser (to complete step 3) and open a new tab to head over to your WordPress website for a minute.</p>\n<p>On your WordPress dashboard, scroll down to the <strong>OptinMonster</strong> tab and click it. You&#8217;ll see your campaign listed. If you don&#8217;t, hit the <strong>Refresh</strong> button until it shows up.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Refresh-Campaigns-1.png\" alt=\"Refresh Campaigns\" width=\"775\" height=\"200\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-227086\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Refresh-Campaigns-1.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Refresh-Campaigns-1-300x77.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Refresh-Campaigns-1-768x198.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Once it appears, click the <strong>Go Live</strong> to enable your campaign on your site.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Go-Live-1.png\" alt=\"Go Live\" width=\"775\" height=\"200\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-227093\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Go-Live-1.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Go-Live-1-300x77.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Go-Live-1-768x198.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>You&#8217;re nearly done! What you just did will enable the popup function of your content upgrade. Now, you&#8217;ll need to place the link on your site to complete the 2-step process for your readers.</p>\n<h3>Step 3: Add Your MonsterLink to Your Site</h3>\n<p>Head back over to the <strong>Publish</strong> page on <a href=\"http://optinmonster.com/\" target=\"_blank\">OptinMonster</a> that you kept open in your browser. </p>\n<p>Scroll down to <strong>Platforms</strong> and choose <strong>Shareable MonsterLink</strong>.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/get-shareable-monsterlink.png\" alt=\"get shareable monsterlink\" width=\"775\" height=\"306\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-227101\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/get-shareable-monsterlink.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/get-shareable-monsterlink-300x118.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/get-shareable-monsterlink-768x303.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>From there, you can copy either the URL or the HTML to paste onto your post or page.</p>\n<p>Personally, we like using the HTML link, as we find it easier to customize per our needs. Just remember to paste it in using the Text editor, rather than the Visual editor.</p>\n<p>For example, you can easily change the default &#8220;Subscribe Now!&#8221; text to your own words. </p>\n<p>Once you have everything looking the way you want it to, publish or update your post or page.</p>\n<p>That&#8217;s it! You now have a content upgrade on your website.</p>\n<p>We hope this tutorial helped you learn how to easily create a content upgrade for your WordPress site.</p>\n<p>If you found this post helpful, you might also enjoy our list of the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-email-marketing-services-compared/\" title=\"9 Best Email Marketing Services Compared\">top email marketing services</a>. After all, you can&#8217;t have a list of subscribers if they have nothing to subscribe to!</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-content-upgrade/\">How to Create a High-Conversion Content Upgrade (Easy Way)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-content-upgrade/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:62:\"How to Get 65% Off Bluehost Web Hosting &amp; Free Domain Name\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:64:\"https://www.isitwp.com/get-free-domain-off-bluehost-web-hosting/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:72:\"https://www.isitwp.com/get-free-domain-off-bluehost-web-hosting/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 10 Jan 2019 10:09:11 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Resources\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"bluehost\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"web hosting\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"wordpress website\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=227942\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:604:\"<p>Are you looking for web hosting for your WordPress website? Bluehost is the best web hosting providers on the market, with top of the line features and services for WordPress users. In this article, we’ll show you how to get a free domain name and 65% off on Bluehost web hosting. Who Is This Plan [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/get-free-domain-off-bluehost-web-hosting/\">How to Get 65% Off Bluehost Web Hosting &#038; Free Domain Name</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7529:\"<p>Are you looking for web hosting for your WordPress website? Bluehost is the best web hosting providers on the market, with top of the line features and services for WordPress users. </p>\n<p>In this article, we’ll show you how to get a free domain name and 65% off on Bluehost web hosting.</p>\n<h3>Who Is This Plan For?</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bluehost</a> is one of the most well-known, reliable <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/hosting-reviews/\">web hosting providers</a> in the world. Their plans work for anyone looking to start a website or blog. From advanced eCommerce websites to humble personal blogs, Bluehost can make your website dreams a reality.</p>\n<p>Or, if you already own a website but aren’t satisfied with the service you’re getting at your current web hosting provider, Bluehost is the perfect choice to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/switch-one-web-host-another-without-downtime-step-by-step/\" title=\"How to Move One Web Host to Another (No Downtime!)\">migrate your website to a reliable host</a>.</p>\n<h3>Why Bluehost?</h3>\n<p>Bluehost web hosting is officially recommended by WordPress.org and is well-known for their stellar <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/hosting-reviews/wordpress/\">WordPress web hosting services</a>. With their 1-click WordPress installations, setting up your first WordPress website has never been easier.</p>\n<p>Unlike other web hosting providers, Bluehost provides a fantastic onboarding experience, making it effortless for anyone to get their WordPress site up-and-running, even if you’re an absolute beginner. </p>\n<p>In addition, Bluehost provides a free domain name and a free <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-add-ssl-and-https-in-wordpress-step-by-step/\" title=\"How to Add SSL and HTTPS in WordPress (Step by Step)\">SSL certificate</a> to their web hosting customers. In other words, you’ll be able to get everything you need to start your website all from the same company.</p>\n<p>And while Bluehost already has amazing prices for the services they provide, IsItWP readers have a chance at an even greater discount. Find out how to take advantage of it below.</p>\n<h3>How to Save 65% on Web Hosting (Step-by-Step)</h3>\n<p>To get started, click on our <strong><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bluehost link</a></strong> to head over to their site and click <strong>Get Started Now</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost.jpg\" alt=\"create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost\" width=\"775\" height=\"483\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-227947\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost-300x187.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost-768x479.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>On the following page, you’ll be shown an assortment of hosting plans. We recommend choosing the Basic plan, since you’re just getting started. This plan includes a free domain and SSL certificate. You can always upgrade your plan later, if needed.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/select-a-bluehost-plan-to-start-a-blog.jpg\" alt=\"select-a-bluehost-plan-to-start-a-blog\" width=\"775\" height=\"483\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-227948\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/select-a-bluehost-plan-to-start-a-blog.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/select-a-bluehost-plan-to-start-a-blog-300x187.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/select-a-bluehost-plan-to-start-a-blog-768x479.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>You’ll then be asked to choose a new domain or enter your existing domain. We recommend nabbing the new domain since it’s free, and choosing a new domain name is fun. If you need help picking out a new domain name, check out our <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/domain-name-generator/\">domain name generator</a>.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/bluehost-domain-purchase.jpg\" alt=\"bluehost-domain-purchase\" width=\"775\" height=\"468\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-227949\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/bluehost-domain-purchase.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/bluehost-domain-purchase-300x181.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/bluehost-domain-purchase-768x464.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>After that, you’ll be asked to enter your account information. To make things extra simple, Bluehost allows you to sign in with your Google account.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/bluehost-account-creation.png\" alt=\"bluehost-account-creation\" width=\"775\" height=\"482\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-227951\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/bluehost-account-creation.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/bluehost-account-creation-300x187.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/bluehost-account-creation-768x478.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Once you’ve entered in your details, scroll down until you locate the package information section. From there, you can select whether you want your Basic plan for 12, 24, or 36 months. We usually opt for the 36 months plan as it gives the most value for the cost.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/bluehost-package-information.jpg\" alt=\"bluehost-package-information\" width=\"775\" height=\"360\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-227950\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/bluehost-package-information.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/bluehost-package-information-300x139.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/bluehost-package-information-768x357.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>You’ll also notice that a few addons have been preselected, which raises the total money owed. Feel free to uncheck these addons as you won’t be needing them if you’re just starting out. You can always purchase them at a later date, if desired.</p>\n<p>Next, enter in your payment information. Finally, check the box agreeing to Bluehost’s Terms of Services, and then click Submit.</p>\n<p>You’re all set! After creating a password for your account, all that’s left to do is wait for an email from Bluehost containing the information on how to log into your control panel (cPanel). You now have a web hosting plan, a domain name, and SSL.</p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you get a massive discount on Bluehost web hosting.</p>\n<p>If you found this article useful, you&#8217;ll also enjoy our step-by-step guide on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-start-a-blog-step-by-step/\" title=\"How to Start a Blog (and Make Extra Income on the Side)\">how to start a blog</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/get-free-domain-off-bluehost-web-hosting/\">How to Get 65% Off Bluehost Web Hosting &#038; Free Domain Name</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:69:\"https://www.isitwp.com/get-free-dom