\"alignnone size-full wp-image-188\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/enter-email.png\" alt=\"Enter your email address to sign in to Google Analytics\" width=\"358\" height=\"380\" /></p>\n<p>Then, you can enter your password and click the <strong>Sign In</strong> button.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-189\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/enter-password.png\" alt=\"Enter your password to sign in to Google Analytics\" width=\"358\" height=\"412\" /></p>\n<p>That’s it! You’re now logged in and should see your dashboard.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-176555\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/ga-analytics-dashboard.jpg\" alt=\"ga-analytics-dashboard\" width=\"550\" height=\"306\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/ga-analytics-dashboard.jpg 550w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/ga-analytics-dashboard-300x167.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p>Now you can find almost any type of analytics data you needs in your Google Analytics dashboard; however, it isn&#8217;t very comprehensive for beginners. There&#8217;s a good chance you&#8217;ll get lost at some point and fail to see the important stats most useful for your business growth.</p>\n<p>But this isn&#8217;t an issue anymore for WordPress users because there&#8217;s a really simple solution available. Continue reading to learn about it.</p>\n<h3>See Your Important Analytics Data in Your WordPress Dashboard</h3>\n<p>Want an easier way to get the data you need directly on your WordPress dashboard, without having to navigate the Google Analytics&#8217; confusing dashboard? Then <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/\">MonsterInsights</a> is the plugin you need!</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-151922\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/monsterinsights-wp-google-analytics-plugin.jpg\" alt=\"monsterinsights-wp-google-analytics-plugin\" width=\"560\" height=\"261\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/monsterinsights-wp-google-analytics-plugin.jpg 560w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/monsterinsights-wp-google-analytics-plugin-300x140.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" /></a></p>\n<p>MonsterInsights is the most user-friendly, most popular Google Analytics plugin for WordPress. Using this plugin, you can easily <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-properly-setup-google-analytics-in-wordpress/\">connect your WordPress site with your Google Analytics account</a> and view your important Analytics data right in your WordPress dashboard. So, you won’t need to login to Google Analytics to view your website&#8217;s data.</p>\n<p>MonsterInsights has a new <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/feature/google-analytics-dashboard/\">Google Analytics dashboard widget</a> feature that lets you view your important website stats right in your WordPress admin page (www.yoursite.com/wp-admin).</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-154759\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/monsterinsightsdashboardwidget.png\" alt=\"Google Analytics Dashboard Widget for WordPress by MonsterInsights\" width=\"620\" height=\"420\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/monsterinsightsdashboardwidget.png 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/monsterinsightsdashboardwidget-300x203.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>That’s not all! You can view a lot more on the MonsterInsights reports page by visiting <strong>Insights » Reports</strong> from your WordPress dashboard.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-157435\" src=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/monsterinsights-overview-report.jpg\" alt=\"monsterinsights-overview-report\" width=\"620\" height=\"575\" srcset=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/monsterinsights-overview-report.jpg 620w, https://www.monsterinsights.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/monsterinsights-overview-report-300x278.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p>For more details, view our <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/your-ultimate-guide-to-monsterinsights-dashboard-reports/\">complete guide on MonsterInsights dashboard reports</a>.</p>\n<p>If you&#8217;re looking for a simple-yet-powerful solution to use Google Analytics in WordPress, MonsterInsights is the best option. <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/\">Give MonsterInsights a try today</a>.</p>\n<p>Like this article? Please follow us on <a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/monsterinsights\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Twitter</a> and <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/monsterinsights\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Facebook</a> for more free tutorials.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-login-to-google-analytics/\">How to Login to Google Analytics (Step by Step)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com\">MonsterInsights</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:70:\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/how-to-login-to-google-analytics/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"\n		\n		\n